POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@mediflow.com",
  "password": "adminpassword"
}

### 4B. Admin accesses restricted endpoint
POST http://localhost:8080/api/hospitals
Content-Type: application/json
Idempotency-Key: 234546
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzM4NCJ9.eyJyb2xlIjoiQURNSU4iLCJzdWIiOiIxIiwiaWF0IjoxNzgxMDEyMzA2LCJleHAiOjE3ODEwOTg3MDZ9.RFv_IOq1xpUlH2_wau0DULRwtsogMhcfihCgskKb7Tp46p7j1cGIGmVFDPh-Px3t

